    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="transcript" id="J369">
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>She lay as if at play</l>
                    <l>Her life had leaped away --</l>
                    <l>Intending to return --</l>
                    <l>But not so soon --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Her merry Arms, half dropt --</l>
                    <l>As if for lull of sport --</l>
                    <l>An instant had forgot</l>
                    <l>The Trick to start --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Her dancing Eyes -- ajar --</l>
                    <l>As if their Owner were</l>
                    <l>Still sparkling through</l>
                    <l>For fun -- at you --</l>
                </lg>
                <lg type="stanza">
                    <l>Her Morning at the door --</l>
                    <l>Devising, I am sure --</l>
                    <l>To force her sleep --</l>
                    <l>So light -- so deep --</l>
                </lg>

            </div>     
